{"tid":1593991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部駐港公署向外媒放話　指反修例歌曲尋求港獨　時代革命等口號顯顏色革命","createTime":"2019-09-25T10:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T10:55:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"de4557d05d8c804d33e0d4e176ca518c4168dc62","tid":1593991,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:29:02.000Z","msg":"香港反送中運動持續，預計 9.28 和 10.1 都有機會再次爆發大規模衝突；外交部駐港特派員公署副特派員宋如安，就向在港外國傳媒放話，指香港示威者揮舞英國、美國國旗，又破壞立法會和中聯辦，貶損國旗和國徽，還唱歌尋求獨立，有「光復香港、時代革命」等口號，是公然挑戰一國兩制紅線，顯露顏色革命和本土恐怖主義的特徵。<br />\n<br />\n宋如安在中環宴請外國傳媒時發言，指持續百多日的示威，除了要求特首林鄭月娥下台，又破壞立法會和中聯辦等，貶損國旗和國徽，煽動學生組人鏈，反修例歌曲是尋求「香港獨立」，口號亦包括「光復香港、時代革命」，「暴徒」的行為令人震驚不可接受，公然挑戰一國兩制紅線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2%E5%90%91%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E6%94%BE%E8%A9%B1-%E6%8C%87%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%9B%B2%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E7%AD%89%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F%E9%A1%AF%E9%A1%8F%E8%89%B2%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD/?fbclid=IwAR3u0x29UJ64OcpJxJv5Y9abNW3vWabp7jYSuQlFD5qgFBFKKPkuGb7SUlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%259B%25B2%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%2591%25BD%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%2599%259F%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E9%25A1%258F%25E8%2589%25B2%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%2591%25BD%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3u0x29UJ64OcpJxJv5Y9abNW3vWabp7jYSuQlFD5qgFBFKKPkuGb7SUlE&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9OzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=0e6bb5b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%2