資訊、冷處理負面POST4.十點咆哮發泄5.思考完就take action<br />\n<strong><em>每星期任務</em></strong>：1. 罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手4.參加一樣民主活動5. 諗下點樣爭取民主<br />\n<strong><em>每月任務</em></strong>：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9OzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=fef55589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9OzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=a8988d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9OzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=86aafc36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.25.2"},{"pid":"2448bf5b24df404cadd21d3d807dcabdcfa138e9","tid":1593991,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"都唔係今日先講架啦，多謝認證，唱多啲"},{"pid":"6fed11d88f536d61459644bf3841a2391b5297c0","tid":1593991,"uid":70127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfd9c41cca078da96ddaae89dcd1bdd8df078f8a","tid":1593991,"uid":65449,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:34:49.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6885503933178f80415a438a35f6fcb01d90fd","tid":1593991,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,